Content:
[dscrd-hush] <ITM> currently Hush(2.25 minutes) -> KMD(1minute) -> BTC(10minutes). So best case is 13.5 minutes for hush to be confirmed with dPOW, Average is more then 20minutes.
Now if Hush(2.25 minutes) -> KMD(1 minute) -> XLM (10 seconds):  So best case is 3.35. Average should be ~5 minutes
But we can just add on top additional dPOW and keep btc as default.
But if exchanges or payment engines decides that XLM is safe they can use the optional dPOW data to get the height.

Its not something important, but its something that possible which is awesome. But we don't need it ðŸ˜› .
Was just for thought moment, Was mention that btc can be replace with anything, but multiple also possible
